    "Management": {
      "text": "Pulmonary consult +/- ID consult\nABPA: Oral\ncorticosteroids\nRecurrent chronic, add oral\nitraconazole\n+/- surgical resection of nasal polyp\nAspergilloma\nSymptomatic (\nhemoptysis\n): Oral\nitraconazole\nIntracavitary CT-guided percutaneous catheter px for\namphotericin B\nSurgical resection\nBronchial artery embolization\nInvasive aspergillosis\nVoriconazole\nDOC\nAlternative: Posaconazole,\namphotericin B\n,\ncaspofungin\nReduce immunosuppression\nCNPA\nVoriconazole\n,\nitraconazole\n,\ncaspofungin\n, or\namphotericin b\nReduce immunosuppression",
